**ArcRaider FPS Booster** is a performance optimization project designed to increase FPS, reduce stuttering, and improve overall system responsiveness in games and high-load applications.

The project focuses on smart resource management, background optimization, and latency reduction to deliver a smoother and more stable gaming experience.

---

## ✨ Key Features

- 🎯 FPS optimization and stability improvements  
- ⚡ Reduced input lag and frame drops  
- 🧠 Smart CPU & RAM resource management  
- 🔕 Background process optimization  
- 🖥️ Optimized for low-end and mid-range systems  
- 🎮 Ideal for competitive and open-world games  

---

## 🔧 How It Works

ArcRaider applies a set of performance-focused tweaks:
- Optimizes system priorities for active applications  
- Reduces unnecessary background load  
- Improves frame consistency under high CPU/GPU usage  
- Enhances overall system responsiveness during gameplay  

---

## 📌 Use Cases

- Gaming performance boost  
- FPS stabilization on weak hardware  
- Reducing micro-stutters and freezes  
- Improving responsiveness in demanding applications  

---

## 📦 Project Status

> 🟢 **Active Development**  
Features and optimizations are continuously being improved.

---


## ⚠️ Disclaimer

This project does **not** modify game files or provide unfair advantages.  
ArcRaider FPS Booster focuses solely on **system-level optimization**.

